 1014.2, 719.9]}, {"text": "2005", "bbox": [1101.1, 703.2, 1133.1, 719.9]}, {"text": "Senior notes due 2013", "bbox": [650.3, 732.4, 790.8, 749.0]}, {"text": "$352.6", "bbox": [971.0, 732.2, 1019.0, 749.0]}, {"text": "$353.0", "bbox": [1094.0, 732.4, 1138.0, 749.0]}, {"text": "Senior notes due 2015", "bbox": [650.3, 753.2, 790.8, 769.9]}, {"text": "250.0", "bbox": [979.0, 753.1, 1019.0, 769.9]}, {"text": "250.0", "bbox": [1102.0, 753.2, 1138.0, 769.9]}, {"text": "Other long-term debt", "bbox": [650.3, 774.0, 779.2, 790.7]}, {"text": "0.4", "bbox": [986.2, 773.9, 1019.0, 790.7]}, {"text": "1.5", "bbox": [1118.0, 774.0, 1138.0, 790.7]}, {"text": "Total long-term debt", "bbox": [650.3, 801.1, 775.4, 817.8]}, {"text": "$603.0", "bbox": [971.0, 801.0, 1019.0, 817.8]}, {"text": "$604.5", "bbox": [1094.0, 801.1, 1138.0, 817.8]}, {"text": "Revolving Credit Facility", "bbox": [650.3, 862.2, 841.4, 883.0]}, {"text": "On January 13, 2005, the Company entered into a 5 year $350.0", "bbox": [650.3, 891.6, 1129.3, 912.4]}, {"text": "unsecured revolving credit facility with Credit Suisse First Boston and", "bbox": [650.3, 920.7, 1152.1, 941.6]}, {"text": "UBS Securities LLC, acting as Co-Lead Arrangers, and a group of", "bbox": [650.3, 949.9, 1125.7, 970.7]}, {"text": "financial institutions for borrowings of up to $350.0. The facility also", "bbox": [650.3, 979.1, 1146.3, 999.9]}, {"text": "provides for an accordion feature whereby the Company can increase", "bbox": [650.3, 1008.2, 1156.5, 1029.1]}, {"text": "the amounts available under the facility up to an additional $150.0,", "bbox": [650.3, 1037.4, 1139.3, 1058.2]}, {"text": "with the consent of the lenders, if needed to support the Company’s", "bbox": [650.3, 1066.6, 1145.0, 1087.4]}, {"text": "growth. There were no balances outstanding on the Company’s", "bbox": [650.3, 1095.7, 1115.5, 1116.6]}, {"text": "revolving credit facility at December 31, 2006 and December 31, 2005.", "bbox": [650.3, 1124.9, 1167.1, 1145.7]}, {"text": "The revolving credit facility bears interest at varying rates based upon", "bbox": [650.3, 1154.1, 1154.6, 1174.9]}, {"text": "the Company’s credit rating with Standard & Poor’s Ratings Services.", "bbox": [650.3, 1183.2, 1155.0, 1204.1]}, {"text": "As of December 31, 2006, the interest rate on the revolving credit", "bbox": [650.3, 1212.4, 1131.7, 1233.2]}, {"text": "facility was 5.8%.", "bbox": [650.3, 1241.6, 783.8, 1262.4]}, {"text": "The senior credit facility is available for general corporate", "bbox": [687.8, 1270.7, 1109.1, 1291.6]}, {"text": "purposes, including working capital, capital expenditures, funding of", "bbox": [650.3, 1299.9, 1152.9, 1320.7]}, {"text": "share repurchases and other payments, and acquisitions. The agree-", "bbox": [650.3, 1329.1, 1154.7, 1349.9]}, {"text": "ment contains certain debt covenants which require that the Company", "bbox": [650.3, 1358.2, 1167.3, 1379.1]}, {"text": "maintain leverage and interest coverage ratios of 2.5 to 1.0 and 5.0", "bbox": [650.3, 1387.4, 1149.8, 1408.2]}, {"text": "to 1.0, respectively. Both ratios are calculated in relation to EBITDA", "bbox": [650.3, 1416.6, 1143.8, 1437.4]}, {"text": "(Earnings Before Interest, Taxes, Depreciation, and Amortization). The", "bbox": [650.3, 1445.7, 1163.6, 1466.6]}, {"text": "covenants also restrict the payment of dividends.  The Company is in", "bbox": [650.3, 1474.9, 1156.2, 1495.7]}, {"text": "compliance with all covenants at December 31, 2006.", "bbox": [650.3, 1504.1, 1046.9, 1524.9]}]}